### 新增用户
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"admin","password":"123456","name":"管理员","email":"admin@test.com"}

### 新增角色
POST http://localhost:8080/role/add
Content-Type: application/json

{"roleName":"管理员","roleCode":"admin","remark":"后台管理"}

### 新增权限
POST http://localhost:8080/permission/add
Content-Type: application/json

{"permissionName":"消息查询","permissionCode":"message:list","remark":"查询消息"}

### 用户绑定角色
POST http://localhost:8080/auth-relation/user-role?userId=1&roleId=1

### 角色绑定权限
POST http://localhost:8080/auth-relation/role-permission?roleId=1&permissionId=1

### 查询用户权限
GET http://localhost:8080/auth-relation/user/1/permission-codes

### 检查用户权限
GET http://localhost:8080/auth-relation/user/1/check?permissionCode=message:list
